## Technical Details

### Tagging Axes
**Axis 1 — Content Type (color tag + text):**
| Type | Finder Color | Extensions |
|------|-------------|------------|
| Photo | Blue | jpg, jpeg, png, heic, raw, dng, etc. |
| Document | Red | pdf, doc, docx, txt, pages, etc. |
| Presentation | Purple | key, pptx, odp |
| Video | Green | mov, mp4, mkv, m4v, etc. |
| Audio | Orange | mp3, m4a, wav, aac, flac, etc. |
| Spreadsheet | Yellow | xls, xlsx, csv, numbers |
| Design | Gray | psd, ai, svg, fig, sketch, etc. |

**Axis 2 — Context/Project (folder name matching):**
Key mappings include: Business, Finance, Personal, Archive, Course, Lecture, Graphic-Asset, Podcast, Video, etc.
- `lecture-outreach/` → Lecture
- `image-bank/` → Lecture, Graphic-Asset
- `icf/` → Podcast
- `podcast/` → Podcast
- `finance/`, `tax/`, `כספים/` → Finance

**Axis 3 — Technical (image analysis via Pillow):**
- `Hi-Res` — longest dimension >= 2000px
- `Lo-Res` — longest dimension < 800px
- `Transparent` — PNG/WEBP with alpha channel
- `raw` — RAW camera format extensions

### iCloud stub detection
Files that are cloud-only stubs (not downloaded) are detected via `st_blocks == 0` and skipped for image analysis.

### Creative Assets Structure
Creates symlinks at `~/Creative-Assets/` organized as:
- Keynote/ (Headshots, Slide-Backgrounds, Icons, Charts, Screenshots)
- Lectures/ (Speaker-Photos, Slides, Handouts, Certificates, Promo-Materials)
- Web-Content/ (Featured-Images, Thumbnails, Banners, Social-Media)
- Podcast/ (Cover-Art, Guest-Photos, Episode-Assets, Promo)
- Finance-Course/ (Slides, Handouts, Marketing, Certificates)
- Social-Media/ (Templates, Quotes, Thumbnails, Brand-Elements)
- Documents/ (Business-CV, Contracts, Insurance, Tax, Certificates)

### APIs & Endpoints
- None (local tool only)
- Uses `tag` CLI: `tag -a {tags} {file1} {file2} ...`
- Uses `tag -f {tag_name} {root}` for finding tagged files

