## Commands
| Command | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `python3 icloud_tagger.py dry-run` | Scan + count files, no changes |
| `python3 icloud_tagger.py tag-fast` | Tag by extension + folder (fast, no image analysis) |
| `python3 icloud_tagger.py tag` | Tag + image analysis via Pillow (slower) |
| `python3 icloud_tagger.py aliases` | Create Creative-Assets folder + populate symlinks |
| `python3 icloud_tagger.py full` | Fast tag + aliases (recommended for regular runs) |
| `python3 icloud_tagger.py full-deep` | Full analysis + tag + aliases (thorough) |
| `brew install tag` | Install required CLI dependency |
| `pip install Pillow` | Install optional image analysis dependency |

